# SSH Client Configuration

# GitHub
Host github.com
    HostName github.com
    User git
    IdentityFile ~/.ssh/id_ed25519
    AddKeysToAgent yes
    UseKeychain yes

# General settings
Host *
    AddKeysToAgent yes
    UseKeychain yes
    IdentitiesOnly yes
    ServerAliveInterval 60
    ServerAliveCountMax 3
